# TypeScript Conventions

- Prefer explicit names over short ambiguous identifiers.
- Shared domain types live in `@driftlands/shared` only — no duplicate models in client/server.
- Validate config with Zod schemas in `shared/src/schemas.ts`.
- Server is authoritative for hazard rolls; client never decides survival.
- Animate UI with GSAP (`useGSAP`, transform/opacity only, `prefers-reduced-motion` via `matchMedia`).
- R3F: instancing, flat/toon materials, no realtime shadow maps in V1.
